WEBVTT

00:12:29.520 --> 00:12:31.216
Da, stvarno to radimo.

00:12:31.240 --> 00:12:34.536
(Smijeh)

00:12:34.560 --> 00:12:37.416
To radimo zato što to otklanja

00:12:37.440 --> 00:12:41.896
ono što smatram
najvećom tragedijom čovječanstva,

00:12:41.920 --> 00:12:44.080
a to je da ljudi arogantno,

00:12:44.760 --> 00:12:49.216
naivno imaju stajališta
koja su kriva,

00:12:49.240 --> 00:12:50.496
i djeluju u skladu s njima

00:12:50.520 --> 00:12:53.280
umjesto da ih preispitaju.

00:12:54.000 --> 00:12:55.336
To je tragedija.

00:12:55.360 --> 00:13:00.776
To radimo jer nas uzdiže
od vlastitih mišljenja